  "detailed_description": "<i>Freakshow came out originally August 2017! This is to celebrate the anniversary of the project!</i><br><br>You go visit the local circus and he takes you. What will you discover?<br><br><br><i>Major updates compared to the original (2017):</i><br>-Achievements <br>-Original soundtrack!<br>-Inventory system<br>-Better voice acting <br>-And more!<br><br><br>Come play a few puzzles and enjoy the mini games!<br><br>Thank you for supporting this game through the development!",
